{"title_page": "Anil Jasinghe", "text_new": "'''Anil Jasinghe''', MD, MSc, MD(MedAd.), MPA, is a vice chairman of World Health Organization<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://apps.who.int/gb/gov/en/chairman-and-officers-of-the-executive-board_en.html|title=WHO {{!}} Chairman and Officers of the Executive Board|website=apps.who.int|access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref> and a Sri Lankan medical administrator who is currently the Director-General of Health Services in Sri Lanka, and the Chief Technical Officer of the [[Ministry of Health, Nutrition and Indigenous Medicine]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Karunaratna |first=Sanchith |url=http://www.adaderana.lk/news/44452/dranil-jasinghe-appointed-as-director-general-of-health-services- |title=Dr.Anil Jasinghe appointed as Director General of Health Services |publisher=Adaderana.lk |date=2017-11-27 |accessdate=2020-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailynews.lk/2017/11/30/local/136042/new-director-general-health-services|title=New Director General of Health Services|website=Daily News}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}<ref name=\":0\" />\n[[Category:Sri Lankan people stubs]]\n[[Category:21st-century Sri Lankan politicians]]\n[[Category:Sri Lankan medical doctors]]\n", "text_old": "'''Anil Jasinghe''', MD, MSc, MD(MedAd.), MPA, is a Sri Lankan medical administrator who is currently the Director-General of Health Services in Sri Lanka, and the Chief Technical Officer of the [[Ministry of Health, Nutrition and Indigenous Medicine]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Karunaratna |first=Sanchith |url=http://www.adaderana.lk/news/44452/dranil-jasinghe-appointed-as-director-general-of-health-services- |title=Dr.Anil Jasinghe appointed as Director General of Health Services |publisher=Adaderana.lk |date=2017-11-27 |accessdate=2020-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailynews.lk/2017/11/30/local/136042/new-director-general-health-services|title=New Director General of Health Services|website=Daily News}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{