=\u0995\u09be\u09a6\u09bf\u09b0 \u0995\u09b2\u09cd\u09b2\u09cb\u09b2 \u09ac\u09bf\u09ac\u09bf\u09b8\u09bf|last1=\u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be|first2=|last2=\u09a2\u09be\u0995\u09be|work=BBC News \u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bd-pratidin.com/special/2018/09/22/362452|title=\u09a1\u09bf\u099c\u09bf\u099f\u09be\u09b2 \u09a8\u09bf\u09b0\u09be\u09aa\u09a4\u09cd\u09a4\u09be \u0986\u0987\u09a8 \u09a8\u09bf\u09af\u09bc\u09c7 \u09a4\u09c3\u09a4\u09c0\u09af\u09bc \u09ae\u09be\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0\u09be\u09af\u09bc \u09af\u09be \u09ac\u09b2\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u09ae\u09be\u09b9\u09ab\u09c1\u099c \u0986\u09a8\u09be\u09ae - \u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b6 \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a4\u09bf\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8|first=Bangladesh|last=Pratidin|publisher=}}</ref>\n| [[Mahfuz Anam]]<ref name=15concerned /><ref name=listof2010editors /><ref name=listof2012editors />\n| 44,814<ref name=BangladeshNewspaperByCirculation/>\n|-\n| {{Sort|Financial Express|''[[Financial Express (Bangladesh)]]''}}<ref name=growth2012 />\n| 1993<ref>{{cite news |last=Khan |first=Maswood Alam |date=2012-04-18 |title=Time to look back and ahead as FE comes of age |url=http://old.thefinancialexpress-bd.com/old/more.php?page=detail_news&date=2012-04-18&news_id=126956 |newspaper=Financial Express}}</ref>\n| International Publications Limited\n| Shahiduzzaman Khan<ref>{{cite news |title=Roundtable stresses guideline to get private sector in CSR funding |url=http://www.thedailystar.net/news-detail-128991 |newspaper=The Daily Star |date=2010-03-06|access-date=2016-05-09}}</ref>\n|39,010<ref name=BangladeshNewspaperByCirculation/>\n|-\n| {{Sort|Daily Sun|''[[Daily Sun (Bangladesh)]]''}}\n|23 October 2010\n| [[East West Media Group]]\n| Enamul Hoque Chowdhury\n|38,800<ref name=BangladeshNewspaperByCirculation/>\n|-\n| {{Sort|The Daily Observer|''[[The Daily Observer (Bangladesh)|The Daily Observer]]''}}\n| 1 February 2011\n| Observer Ltd\n| [[Iqbal Sobhan Chowdhury]]\n|38,7